Overview of changes from gnome-directory-thumbnailer 0.1.3 to 0.1.4
===================================================================

Major changes:
 • Add a note about uninstallation to the README — packagers please note that
   the user’s thumbnail cache directories should be cleared on uninstallation

Updated translations:
 • fr (Alain Lojewski)
 • id (Andika Triwidada)


